data.name: Feasting at Home Recipes
data.description: Browse hundreds of Veggie-Driven, plant-based recipes from Feasting at Home - a whole foods recipe blog by chef, Sylvia Fountaine, featuring fresh seasonal local produce!

data.name: Healthy Salad Recipes - Feasting at Home
data.description: Healthy Delicious Salad Recipes filled with fresh and vibrant summer salads! Packed full of seasonal and healthy veggies perfect for lunches or summer dinners. Easy and simple, with many vegan and vegetarian options!

data.name: Healthy Snack Recipes
data.description: Some of my favorite simple, delicious snack recipes! Here you'll find a variety of healthy snack options that you can take with you while you're on the go. Everything from hummus to granola bars.

data.name: Fresh and Tasty Mexican Recipes (Cinco De Mayo!)
data.description: Whether you are celebrating Cinco De Mayo or are having a simple family gathering at home, here are Best Mexican Recipes to create the perfect Mexican Feast. Packed full of healthy veggies with authentic flavors, pick out a few to try this week!

data.name: Side Dish Recipes
data.description: Recipes for simple, healthy side dishes with many vegan, vegetarian and gluten-free options!

data.name: Healthy Grilling Recipes
data.description: Fire up the barbecue! These delicious summer grilling recipes are light, healthy and perfect all summer long! Find delicious main, salads and sides including vegan, vegetarian and gluten free options!

data.name: Asian Inspired Recipes
data.description: Simple, healthy Asian Recipes perfect for weeknight dinners! Find healthy and comforting versions of your favorite take out.

data.name: Gluten-Free Recipes
data.description: Delicious and healthy gluten-free recipes from my blog and around the web! Who knew gluten-free could be this delicious?

data.name: Healthy Bowls!
data.description: Fresh, healthy, plant-based Buddha bowls to heal, nourish and energize. Vegan and gluten-free adaptable.  Great for mixed households.... where both vegans and meat-eaters reside. Clean-eating!

data.name: Summer Recipes
data.description: The best collection of seasonal summer recipes using fresh and seasonal summer ingredients. Find healthy summer salads, tasty summer sides, delicious and easy healthy grilled veggies and lean meats including grilled summer chicken breast recipes and seasonal summer fruit inspired desserts.
